## Proposed Changes

### Fase 1: Fix Data Yang Tidak Muncul (CRITICAL)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Ini adalah fix **blocking** — tanpa ini, 6+ screen menampilkan data kosong.

#### [MODIFY] Semua screen dengan `fetchData()` yang tidak dipanggil

Konversi semua screen dari pattern `fetchData + useState` ke `useQuery`:

**Piket Dashboard** — [dashboard.tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/mobile-app/app/(piket)/dashboard.tsx)
```diff
- const [pendingTickets, setPendingTickets] = useState<any[]>([]);
- const [dailyLogs, setDailyLogs] = useState<any[]>([]);
- const fetchData = async () => { ... };
+ const { data: pendingTickets = [] } = useQuery({
+   queryKey: ['dispensasi-pending'],
+   queryFn: () => api.get('/dispensasi/pending').then(r => r.data),
+ });
+ const { data: dailyLogData } = useQuery({
+   queryKey: ['piket-daily-log'],
+   queryFn: () => api.get('/piket/daily-log').then(r => r.data),
+ });
```

**Piket Queue** — [queue.tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/SIdispen%20(SMA%203)/mobile-app/app/(piket)/queue.tsx)
```diff
- const [tickets, setTickets] = useState<any[]>([]);
- const fetchData = async () => { ... };
+ const { data: rawTickets = [], isLoading: loading } = useQuery({
+   queryKey: ['dispensasi-all'],
+   queryFn: () => api.get('/dispensasi').then(r => r.data),
+ });
+ const tickets = rawTickets.filter(t => 
+   (t.status === 'pending' || t.status === 'approved_by_wali') && isToday(t.created_at)
+ );
```

