### Fase 4: Mutation + Cache Invalidation

Semua tindakan mutasi harus di-wrap dengan `useMutation` agar otomatis invalidate query terkait:

| Action | Endpoint | Invalidate Keys |
|--------|----------|-----------------|
| Submit dispensasi | `POST /dispensasi` | `['dispensasi-me']` |
| Approve ticket | `POST /dispensasi/{id}/approve` | `['dispensasi-pending']`, `['dispensasi-all']`, `['dispensasi', id]`, `['piket-daily-log']` |
| Reject ticket | `POST /dispensasi/{id}/reject` | `['dispensasi-pending']`, `['dispensasi-all']`, `['dispensasi', id]` |
| Validate QR | `POST /piket/validate-qr` | `['piket-daily-log']`, `['dispensasi-all']` |
| Toggle piket status | `POST /piket/status` | `['piket-status']` |
| Send chat | `POST /dispensasi/{id}/chats` | Handled by Supabase realtime ✅ |

